OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FBy Emily Youlton, Senior Politics
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FThe government has launched it's
OL,10,F"Great British Summer Savings" scheme,
OL,11,Fproviding cheaper tickets and free bus
OL,12,Ftravel with an aim to help families
OL,13,Fget "money off trips out with the
OL,14,Fkids".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
