FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FThe prime minister has said these
OL,7,Fmeasures are to help tackle the cost
OL,8,Fof living and giving families "the
OL,9,Fopportunity to take the kids out", but
OL,10,Fit has been met with some criticism
OL,11,Fthat it's not as beneficial for
OL,12,Ffamilies on the lowest incomes.
OL,14,FAt the launch of the scheme, the
OL,15,FChancellor, Rachel Reeves, said she
OL,16,Fwants "every family to be able to
OL,17,Fenjoy themselves".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FThe plan will cut VAT from 20% to 5%
OL,7,Fon ticket prices for both adults and
OL,8,Fchildren for attractions such as
OL,9,Ffairs, theme parks, zoos and museums,
OL,10,Fas well as on children's tickets for
OL,11,Fcinemas, concerts, soft play, theatre
OL,12,Fand meals in restaurants and cafes.
OL,14,FThe scheme runs between June 25 to
OL,15,FSeptember 1.
OL,17,FSo, what actually are the savings and
OL,18,Fhow can you benefit? ITV News explains
OL,19,Fwhere and how families can make the
OL,20,Fmost of these savings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FThe government announcement provides a
OL,7,Fcut to VAT on a variety of tickets and
OL,8,Fchildren's meals across the UK from
OL,9,Fthe usual 20% to 5%, so businesses can
OL,10,Fchoose to pass that saving on to
OL,11,Fcustomers by reducing the price.
OL,13,FChildren's and family tickets are
OL,14,Fincluded in the tax cut for cinemas,
OL,15,Ftheatres, concerts, shows and
OL,16,Fexhibitions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FPlus, tickets for both children and
OL,7,Fadults are exempt on attractions
OL,8,Fincluding amusement parks, fairs,
OL,9,Fmuseums, zoos, soft play centres,
OL,10,Fcircuses, adventure parks, nature
OL,11,Freserves, wildlife parks and
OL,12,Fobservation attractions.
OL,14,FMany big entertainment brands have
OL,15,Fpraised the initiative and said
OL,16,Fthey'll be taking part, including
OL,17,Fcinemas Odeon and Vue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
