PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FLots of other entertainment parks will
OL,7,Freduce prices, like those in the
OL,8,FBritish Association of Leisure Parks,
OL,9,FPiers and Attractions, which includes
OL,10,Fbig names like Thorpe Park, Longleat
OL,11,Fand Peppa Pig World.
OL,13,FThe savings on an advanced ticket
OL,14,Fbooked online for Thorpe Park would be
OL,15,Fjust under #5 down from #34 to #29.75.
OL,17,FA ticket to Longleat for a family of
OL,18,Ftwo adults and two children could save
OL,19,F#17.50 on their cheapest tickets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
