PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FThe VAT reduction also applies to
OL,7,Fchildren's meals served in restaurants
OL,8,Fand eaten in, so takeaway's do not
OL,9,Fcount.
OL,11,FThis should mean cheaper food for
OL,12,Fchildren when eating out as the VAT is
OL,13,F15% less but it doesn't apply to adult
OL,14,Fmeals or to any meal that's not
OL,15,Fspecifically from a children's menu.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
