OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FEvery child aged five to 15 in England
OL,7,Fcan access free bus travel on
OL,8,Fparticipating local routes, with more
OL,9,Fthan #100 million being spent to fund
OL,10,Fit and support bus services facing
OL,11,Fincreased costs.
OL,13,FThis excludes London, where under-18's
OL,14,Falready have year round free travel on
OL,15,FTfL buses and trams and discounted
OL,16,Ffares on the Tube, DLR and Overground.
OL,18,FThe other Home Nations don't have any
OL,19,Fchanges to their travel as many
OL,20,Falready offer transport discounts to
OL,21,Fchildren and young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
