PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1782427691
OL,3,CHow can you save money with the 'Great
OL,4,CBritish Summer Savings' scheme?
OL,6,FWales offers five to 15 year olds #1
OL,7,Fsingle fares on bus and capped day
OL,8,Ftickets for #3. In addition, 16-21
OL,9,Fyear olds can also get reduced fares
OL,10,Fby applying for a MyTravelPass.
OL,12,FIn Scotland, anyone aged between five
OL,13,Fto 21 years can travel free on most
OL,14,Flocal and long-distance buses.
OL,16,FIn Northern Ireland, children aged
OL,17,Ffive to 15 (and 16-year olds in
OL,18,Fschool) are entitled to half-price
OL,19,Ffares on buses if they apply for a
OL,20,FHalf Fare Smart Pass.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
